Foghorn.Data.Comp.Funda

Description

This module defines the variable set for Compustat North America Fundamentals Annual (FUNDA), represented as a GADT (FundaV). Each constructor corresponds to a named variable and is indexed by an EconType (e.g., Float_, Int_, Text_, Date_).
